Package: obs-snekstudio-source
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, obs-studio, python3
Description: OBS Studio plugin and demo publisher for cooperative SnekStudio capture
 This package installs the SnekStudio OBS source plugin, the reference
 shared-memory frame protocol header, and a demo publisher binary used for
 local testing before the real SnekStudio-side integration exists.